    </div>

    <div class="space-y-8 text-neutral-300">

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">FTC Disclosure</h2>
        <p class="leading-relaxed">
          In accordance with the FTC's guidelines, TobyOnFitnessTech discloses that some links on this website are affiliate links. At this time, this applies only to Amazon Associates links. If you click these links and make a qualifying purchase, I may receive compensation at no additional cost to you.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Amazon</h2>
        <p class="leading-relaxed">
          This site participates in the Amazon Associates Program. Links to products on Amazon may be affiliate links. As an Amazon Associate, I earn from qualifying purchases.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Editorial Independence</h2>
        <p class="leading-relaxed">
          Affiliate relationships do not influence editorial content. I have received no free products or payments in exchange for positive coverage. All products reviewed were purchased with my own money unless explicitly stated otherwise.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed">
          If that ever changes, it will be disclosed clearly in the relevant content.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Questions</h2>
        <p class="leading-relaxed">
          Questions about affiliate relationships? Email <a href="mailto:admin@tobyonfitnesstech.com" class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300">admin@tobyonfitnesstech.com</a>.
        </p>
      </section>

    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
